de.oaam.model.oaam.library

Interface ResourceBundles

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementA, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ResourceConsumerA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResourceBundlesImpl

    public interface ResourceBundles
extends ResourceConsumerA, ElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Resource Bundles'. This are installable portions of resources

    The following features are supported:

    • Resources
    • Mtbf
    • Cost
    • Mass
    See Also:
    LibraryPackage.getResourceBundles()
